reviews.review_text: My Favorite Tape I did not go to this show.  I received a tape when I was in high school in 97 or 98.  It quickly became a favorite.  I would listen to set 2 in particular on runs, the ebbs and flows were just perfect to keep me going.  I know its not close to the best show, or best recording, or anything like that, but I have loved it for many years.  Thank you for letting me find it again.
First show All around great show. Pretty good list, great performance. I think this is the best sounding audience tape. I was 17 and it was a turning point for me.
